00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:04,420
Which one?

576
00:22:04,420 --> 00:22:04,720
This one,

577
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,080
I think.

578
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,080
H dagger here.

579
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:10,400
All right,

