587
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,580
And then from here times one,

588
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,800
we'll have H bar,

589
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:28,800
sorry,

590
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:29,420
H dagger.

591
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,940
But from one times here,

592
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,620
we will have minus H.

593
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:41,140
One times the minus H,

594
00:22:41,140 --> 00:22:43,720
and then the H dagger times the one.

595
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:45,660
Those are the two terms that appear here.

596
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:46,400
Oh,

597
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:47,480
we left out the one.

598
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:48,520
One times one is one,

599
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:50,420
but that cancels the one here.

600
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:54,920
So the result is the condition that U be unitary

601
00:22:56,580 --> 00:23:01,300
is the condition that H dagger equals H.

602
00:23:02,180 --> 00:23:05,080
Or H dagger minus H equals zero.

603
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:08,440
Same thing as saying H dagger equals H.

604
00:23:11,360 --> 00:23:12,520
In other words,

605
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,380
whatever H is,

606
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:15,800
