607
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:17,700
That,

608
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:18,100
of course,

609
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:20,640
is the condition that H is Hermitian.

610
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:26,140
So what we learn from this basic principle

611
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:29,860
that relationships have to be invariant

612
00:23:29,860 --> 00:23:31,060
under time evolution,

613
00:23:31,060 --> 00:23:32,820
relationships of vectors,

614
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:36,280
is we learn that for a small interval of time,

615
00:23:36,580 --> 00:23:38,420
the evolution procedure

616
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:41,700
