629
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,560
All of its eigenvalues are real.

630
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:12,200
And it's something which can be measured in the laboratory.

631
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:13,900
That's what it means to be observable.

632
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:15,980
The postulate of quantum mechanics

633
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:17,400
