00:24:36,620 --> 00:24:38,400
it's some physical quantity.

641
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,760
The interpretation of it,

642
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:43,620
now,

643
00:24:43,620 --> 00:24:44,560
we can give it a name.

