00:24:47,780 --> 00:24:49,580
are the things that you measure

647
00:24:49,580 --> 00:24:51,180
when you measure H.

648
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,680
Its eigenvalues have a name.

649
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,340
