00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:45,540
the expectation value of H,

674
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:46,520
the average of H,

675
00:25:47,699 --> 00:25:50,600
evolves or behaves exactly the same way,

676
00:25:50,620 --> 00:25:52,560
has the same value as

677
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:54,500
the classical energy of a system,

678
00:25:54,660 --> 00:25:56,660
or approximately the same value.

679
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:57,820
But not for now.

680
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:58,200
For now,

681
00:25:58,200 --> 00:26:00,500
we are just going to call the eigenvalues the energy,

