00:26:07,740 --> 00:26:10,360
we have learned a new principle

685
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:14,760
that the Hermitian operator called the Hamiltonian,

686
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:18,540
which governs the evolution of a system

687
00:26:18,540 --> 00:26:20,260
as it evolves in time.

688
00:26:20,700 --> 00:26:22,440
Are there any questions up until now?

689
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:25,480
Now,

690
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,780
if we know how a system evolves

