822
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,100
If we can predict what it's going to be

823
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,400
in the next instant of time,

824
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:11,080
we can do next instant,

825
00:31:11,080 --> 00:31:11,740
next instant,

826
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:12,360
next instant,

