831
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:25,880
This equation has a name.

832
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,800
Anybody know the name of it?

833
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,180
That's the Schrodinger equation.

834
00:31:30,220 --> 00:31:31,420
That's the Schrodinger equation.

835
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:34,880
It's the abstract general form of the Schrodinger equation.

836
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:37,840
It's not the equation Schrodinger wrote down.

837
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:39,380
To my knowledge,

838
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,660
I think the first one to write it

