00:32:03,020 --> 00:32:07,480
is the Hamiltonian operator times psi.

849
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:14,180
That's sort of very similar to this formula.

850
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:17,540
This said that a derivative with respect to position

