00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,580
is related in a similar way to the energy,

854
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:27,920
to the Hamiltonian.

855
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,740
Notice there's a difference in sign.

856
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:32,580
This is purely a convention.

857
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,690
That there's a minus sign

858
00:32:34,690 --> 00:32:36,120
here and a plus sign here.

