1993
01:15:57,186 --> 01:15:57,886
But for now,

1994
01:15:57,886 --> 01:16:01,706
and this was a very easy derivation.

1995
01:16:01,766 --> 01:16:02,726
This was very simple.

1996
01:16:02,886 --> 01:16:03,426
What did we do?

1997
01:16:03,506 --> 01:16:04,646
Let me just remind you what we did.

1998
01:16:05,066 --> 01:16:07,156
We time differentiated this by

1999
01:16:07,156 --> 01:16:09,246
