2005
01:16:21,226 --> 01:16:22,606
The opposite sign,

2006
01:16:22,606 --> 01:16:25,066
which appears here because of the complex conjugate,

2007
01:16:25,866 --> 01:16:27,926
wound up giving us a commutator.

2008
01:16:29,326 --> 01:16:30,806
So it's very two lines,

2009
01:16:30,806 --> 01:16:32,086
two lines basically,

2010
01:16:33,145 --> 01:16:36,005
to derive the connection between

2011
01:16:36,005 --> 01:16:38,866
time derivatives and commutators with Hamiltonians.

2012
01:16:39,466 --> 01:16:40,486
We could,

