2024
01:16:56,226 --> 01:16:58,356
So we proved the theorem that said

2025
01:16:58,356 --> 01:17:00,486
that the time derivative of any expectation value

2026
01:17:01,046 --> 01:17:03,126
is related to a certain commutator,

2027
01:17:03,126 --> 01:17:06,106
commutator of the Hamiltonian with the quantity in question.

