01:17:13,726 --> 01:17:15,266
if the commutator is zero,

2032
01:17:15,586 --> 01:17:18,016
then the time derivative of

2033
01:17:18,016 --> 01:17:20,446
its expectation value is exactly zero.

2034
01:17:21,086 --> 01:17:23,386
Exactly zero in any state.

2035
01:17:24,126 --> 01:17:25,466
In any state,

2036
01:17:25,466 --> 01:17:28,986
