I'd like to prove a somewhat stronger theorem.

2044
01:17:47,446 --> 01:17:49,166
The stronger theorem might

2045
01:17:49,166 --> 01:17:50,886
say that the probability distribution

2046
01:17:50,886 --> 01:17:52,856
