2076
01:18:50,906 --> 01:18:56,386
So it implies that the Hamiltonian itself is conserved.

2077
01:18:56,766 --> 01:18:59,846
The Hamiltonian is some kind of conserved quantity.

2078
01:19:00,586 --> 01:19:02,766
Let me just point out the classical analog.

2079
01:19:03,226 --> 01:19:06,096
The classical analog is that the Poisson bracket

2080
01:19:06,096 --> 01:19:08,966
