2082
01:19:10,486 --> 01:19:12,006
Let's take some object A.

2083
01:19:13,826 --> 01:19:15,806
That's dA by dX,

2084
01:19:15,806 --> 01:19:17,726
dB by dP,

2085
01:19:17,726 --> 01:19:22,566
minus dA by dP,

2086
01:19:22,566 --> 01:19:25,406
dB by dX.

2087
01:19:25,726 --> 01:19:27,666
That's the Poisson bracket of A with B.

2088
01:19:28,126 --> 01:19:29,706
If A and B are equal,

2089
01:19:29,706 --> 01:19:32,226
then obviously this is equal to zero.

2090
01:19:32,566 --> 01:19:35,106
dA by dX is the same as dB by dX,

2091
01:19:35,126 --> 01:19:36,276
and dB by dP is

2092
01:19:36,276 --> 01:19:37,426
the same as dA by dP,

2093
01:19:37,506 --> 01:19:39,186
so that this is equal to zero.

2094
01:19:39,626 --> 01:19:40,146
Again,

2095
01:19:40,146 --> 01:19:41,546
in classical physics,

2096
01:19:41,546 --> 01:19:42,946
it follows that

2097
01:19:42,946 --> 01:19:46,346
any quantity whose Poisson bracket with the

2098
01:19:46,346 --> 01:19:49,746
Hamiltonian is equal to zero is conserved.

2099
01:19:49,886 --> 01:19:51,626
Its time derivative is equal to zero.

2100
01:19:51,866 --> 01:19:52,946
And in particular,

2101
01:19:52,946 --> 01:19:58,246
the Hamiltonian is a quantity which commutes...

2102
01:19:58,246 --> 01:19:58,386
Oh,

2103
01:19:58,386 --> 01:19:58,706
sorry.

2104
01:19:59,046 --> 01:20:00,896
...is a quantity whose Poisson bracket

2105
01:20:00,896 --> 01:20:02,746
with itself is equal to zero,

2106
01:20:02,946 --> 01:20:05,986
and so it follows that the Hamiltonian is conserved.

2107
01:20:06,346 --> 01:20:07,546
In quantum mechanics,

2108
01:20:07,546 --> 01:20:08,846
it's the commutator,

2109
01:20:08,846 --> 01:20:10,206
but same statement.

2110
01:20:10,786 --> 01:20:12,646
If a quantity commutes with...

2111
01:20:12,946 --> 01:20:14,566
If a quantity commutes with a Hamiltonian...

2112
01:20:14,566 --> 01:20:15,506
I'm saying it over and over.

2113
01:20:15,726 --> 01:20:17,486
If a quantity commutes with a Hamiltonian,

2114
01:20:17,486 --> 01:20:18,086
it's conserved.

2115
01:20:18,086 --> 01:20:19,846
The Hamiltonian commutes with a Hamiltonian,

2116
01:20:19,846 --> 01:20:20,646
the Hamiltonian is conserved.

