2127
01:20:46,586 --> 01:20:50,066
Let's now come to a particle on a line.

2128
01:20:51,246 --> 01:20:52,626
Particle moving on a line.

2129
01:20:53,346 --> 01:20:53,726
Now,

2130
01:20:53,726 --> 01:20:56,166
what is the connection...

2131
01:20:56,166 --> 01:20:56,346
Well,

2132
01:20:56,346 --> 01:20:57,006
first of all,

2133
01:20:57,006 --> 01:20:58,946
let's just have a particle moving on a line.

2134
01:20:59,106 --> 01:21:00,506
No potential energy,

2135
01:21:00,506 --> 01:21:02,426
