01:21:39,526 --> 01:21:46,256
We would like to find some way of thinking about the

2150
01:21:46,256 --> 01:21:52,986
time derivative of psi of x and t with respect to t.

2151
01:21:54,366 --> 01:21:55,006
Now,

2152
01:21:55,006 --> 01:21:56,406
what we're doing is we're doing

