01:22:15,106 --> 01:22:17,346
And so for a particle on a line,

2162
01:22:17,686 --> 01:22:19,666
the state vector can simply

2163
01:22:19,666 --> 01:22:21,646
be replaced by a wave function,

2164
01:22:21,846 --> 01:22:23,466
which depends on x and t,

2165
01:22:23,646 --> 01:22:25,926
or its Fourier transform,

