01:22:25,926 --> 01:22:28,586
which depends on momentum and also t.

2167
01:22:29,466 --> 01:22:31,226
How do they evolve with time?

2168
01:22:32,126 --> 01:22:33,526
They must evolve with time

2169
01:22:33,526 --> 01:22:34,926
by the same set of rules,

2170
01:22:36,146 --> 01:22:37,046
minus i,

2171
01:22:37,586 --> 01:22:39,766
