2173
01:22:45,325 --> 01:22:47,926
acting on psi of x and t.

2174
01:22:50,766 --> 01:22:52,286
Same set of arguments.

2175
01:22:53,666 --> 01:22:57,686
And I've simply just removed the brackets here

