2195
01:23:37,586 --> 01:23:38,226
with respect to x.

2196
01:23:38,346 --> 01:23:39,426
They're all linear operators.

2197
01:23:39,986 --> 01:23:43,086
They're all linear operators on these psi of x's here.

2198
01:23:43,186 --> 01:23:43,726
For example,

