2588
01:38:04,746 --> 01:38:07,306
Does the probability for a given position vary with time?

2589
01:38:07,306 --> 01:38:08,926
But we'll deal with that next time.

2590
01:38:13,426 --> 01:38:14,006
Incidentally,

2591
01:38:14,006 --> 01:38:16,906
you might want to prove to yourself

2592
01:38:16,906 --> 01:38:19,806
